description:
If you’re doing more than an M-check, it is nice to have full size Torx keys. These 4 Torx keys have you covered for most of your bike needs, swap rotors, index your derailleur, fine tune your cockpit, etc.

  • Includes: Torx™ T15, T20, T25 and T30
  • Made of hardened tool steel
  • Ring carrier keeps Torx keys together
  • Durable black coating reduces corrosion
name: MEC 4-Piece Torx Key Set
